1. git clone the-project-url on github
2.cd to project and run: docker compose up -d --build


Steps for creating a common network
1. docker network create --attachable -d bridge vuejsspringv2
2. docker run -it -d --name psql-vue-spring-container -p 5434:5432 --network vuejsspringv2 -e POSTGRES_PASSWORD=example --restart always -v postgresql_data_container:/var/lib/postgresql postgres:latest
3. docker run -it -d --name spring-vue-adminer -p 9090:8080 --network vuejsspringv2 -e ADMINER_DEFAULT_SERVER=psql-vue-spring-container --restart always adminer:latest

